    "description": "<p>Founded in 1924, Popular Holdings Limited is a multi-faceted conglomerate with businesses in a wide-ranging number of sectors, such as Retail, e-Commerce, Publishing, Education, Distribution, Purchasing, e-Learning, and more. Our diverse portfolio consists of more than 40 subsidiaries operating in Singapore, Malaysia, Hong Kong, Macau, Taiwan, China, Canada, Australia, and United Kingdom. For close to a century, we’ve committed ourselves to empowering our people by encouraging a sense of ownership towards their responsibilities and involving them in the decision-making process. This helps establish a culture of staff-driven change that is highly attuned to the evolving consumer landscapes and industry trends, which helps us maintain our strong presence and competitive edge.</p>",
